latestIgtvVideos.title: Instagram Content Theft
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
As a micro blogger, my content has often been lifted off my page and posted by other users. So I decided to send this message out after sharing it earlier on my stories. 

▪️When you don’t create original content and post someone else’s photos, images or descriptions by unethical means, it’s not them that you’re harming. 

▪️It’s your own creativity that you are denting which might never take flight because you never gave it a chance. 

▪️You’re depriving your brand of finding its own niche, originality and identity. 

(That scrunchie is from @puruessentials 🙂)

Issued in PSA. 
Big thank you to all the co bloggers who have time and again alerted me by sharing content thefts. 💜

#skincare #skin #skinjourney #contentcreator #content #brand #branding #brandidentity #contenttheft #hack #unethical #thankyou #gratitude #blogger #bloggerstyle #blog
